      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以Infra_WorkerNode是起点，然后进入NeedMore状态。NeedMore自己会循环吗？比如持续接收输入的情况？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "NeedMore"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，NeedMore可以自循环，标注为\"more input\"。另外还需要两个出口：一个是收到EOF或完成时转到Complete，另一个是出错时转到Error。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NeedMore",
