        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主结构：从Infra_WorkerNode指向NeedMore，然后NeedMore自循环标\"more input\"，再分出两条线到Complete和Error。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "NeedMore",
        "Complete",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "NeedMore到Complete的转移条件应该是\"EOF/complete\"，注意斜杠两边都要保留。Error状态就是简单的\"error\"触发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NeedMore",
        "Complete",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：NeedMore→Complete标\"EOF/complete\"，NeedMore→Error标\"error\"，NeedMore自循环标\"more input\"。这样三条转移关系对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
